title: Strife: Day of the Acolyte and Return of the Order playthroughs
description: Day of the Acolyte was awesome and fun. Return of the Order was way too hard. I still enjoyed the map and think it was pretty cool, but the lack of ammunition was pretty stupid. Would be worth playing on an easier difficulty (not skill 4). I cheated at the end of Return of the Order just to see the end of it.
